<main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-7">
  <h1 class="font-bold text-lg md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl">Buat Modul Ajar secara cepat dan efisien<br/>dengan bantuan teknologi berbasis AI (Akal Imitasi)</h1>
  <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Quia atque modi praesentium, itaque ex, fugiat similique ducimus labore expedita a ipsum culpa, eaque sint? Dicta similique at eius a natus!</p>

  <div class="mt-10 border-2 md:border-4 border-dashed p-5">
    <div class="text-gray-700">
      <p>Tolong isi beberapa kolom dibawah ini untuk membantu AI membuat dokumen.</p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-1 font-bold mt-1">
        Gunakan tombol
        <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-400 border border-gray-500 p-1 rounded">
          <%- include('components/icons/bsstars.ejs', {width: "16px", height: "16px"}) %>
        </span>
        untuk menyempurnakan kalimat dengan bantuan AI.
      </div>
    </div>

    <form action="" method="post" class="mt-5">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-10 w-full">

        <label class="group block cursor-pointer" for="namaSekolah">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-sky-800">
            <%- include('components/icons/school.ejs', {width: "20px", height: "20px"}) %> 
            <span>Satuan Pendidikan</span>
          </div>
          <small class="text-sm text-gray-500">Boleh dikosongkan</small>
          
          <input type="text" name="namaSekolah" id="namaSekolah" 
            class="w-full border-2 border-sky-800/50 rounded-md p-2 mt-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-sky-800 focus:border-transparent" 
            placeholder="Contoh: SDN 1 Cibodas">
        </label>

        <label class="group block cursor-pointer" for="namaPenyusun">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-green-800">
            <%- include('components/icons/user.ejs', {width: "20px", height: "20px"}) %> 
            <span>Nama Penyusun</span>
          </div>
          <small class="text-sm text-gray-500">Boleh dikosongkan</small>
          
          <input type="text" name="namaPenyusun" id="namaPenyusun" 
            class="w-full border-2 border-green-800/50 rounded-md p-2 mt-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-green-800 focus:border-transparent" 
            placeholder="Contoh: Budi Santoso">
        </label>

        <label class="group block cursor-pointer" for="nip">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-yellow-800">
            <%- include('components/icons/number.ejs', {width: "20px", height: "20px"}) %> 
            <span>NIP</span>
          </div>
          <small class="text-sm text-gray-500">Boleh dikosongkan</small>
          
          <input type="text" name="nip" id="nip" 
            class="w-full border-2 border-yellow-800/50 rounded-md p-2 mt-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-yellow-800 focus:border-transparent" 
            placeholder="Contoh: 1234567890">
        </label>

        <label class="group block cursor-pointer" for="fase">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-red-800">
            <%- include('components/icons/phase.ejs', {width: "20px", height: "20px"}) %> 
            <span>Fase</span>
          </div>
          <small class="text-sm text-gray-500">Pilih Fase yang sesuai</small>
          
          <select name="fase" id="fase" 
            class="w-full border-2 border-red-800/50 rounded-md p-2 mt-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-800 focus:border-transparent appearance-none cursor-pointer" required>
            <option value="Fondasi" selected>Fondasi</option>
          </select>
        </label>

        <label class="group block cursor-pointer" for="semester">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-violet-800">
            <%- include('components/icons/date.ejs', {width: "20px", height: "20px"}) %> 
            <span>Semester</span>
          </div>
          <small class="text-sm text-gray-500">Semester saat ini</small>
          
          <input type="number" name="semester" id="semester" 
            class="w-full border-2 border-violet-800/50 rounded-md p-2 mt-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-violet-800 focus:border-transparent" 
            placeholder="Contoh: 2" min="1" max="14" required>
        </label>

        <label class="group block cursor-pointer" for="bulan">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-purple-800">
            <%- include('components/icons/date.ejs', {width: "20px", height: "20px"}) %> 
            <span>Bulan</span>
          </div>
          <small class="text-sm text-gray-500">Pilih bulan pelaksanaan</small>
          
          <select name="bulan" id="bulan" 
            class="w-full border-2 border-purple-800/50 rounded-md p-2 mt-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-800 focus:border-transparent appearance-none cursor-pointer" required>
            <option value="Januari" selected>Januari</option>
            <option value="Februari">Februari</option>
            <option value="Maret">Maret</option>
            <option value="April">April</option>
            <option value="Mei">Mei</option>
            <option value="Juni">Juni</option>
            <option value="Juli">Juli</option>
            <option value="Agustus">Agustus</option>
            <option value="September">September</option>
            <option value="Oktober">Oktober</option>
            <option value="November">November</option>
            <option value="Desember">Desember</option>
          </select>
        </label>

        <label class="group block cursor-pointer" for="mingguKe">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-violet-800">
            <%- include('components/icons/date.ejs', {width: "20px", height: "20px"}) %> 
            <span>Minggu Ke</span>
          </div>
          <small class="text-sm text-gray-500">Minggu ke berapa dalam pembelajaran kali ini</small>
          
          <input type="number" name="mingguKe" id="mingguKe" 
            class="w-full border-2 border-violet-800/50 rounded-md p-2 mt-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-violet-800 focus:border-transparent" 
            placeholder="Contoh: 2" min="1" max="4" required>
        </label>

        <label class="group block cursor-pointer" for="kelas">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-red-800">
            <%- include('components/icons/phase.ejs', {width: "20px", height: "20px"}) %> 
            <span>Kelas</span>
          </div>
          <small class="text-sm text-gray-500">Pilih Kelas yang sesuai</small>
          
          <select name="kelas" id="kelas" 
            class="w-full border-2 border-red-800/50 rounded-md p-2 mt-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-800 focus:border-transparent appearance-none cursor-pointer" required>
            <option value="Kelompok A (4-5 tahun)" selected>Kelompok A (4-5 tahun)</option>
            <option value="Kelompok B (5-6 tahun)">Kelompok B (5-6 tahun)</option>
          </select>
        </label>

        <label class="group block cursor-pointer" for="jumlahAnak">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-violet-800">
            <%- include('components/icons/date.ejs', {width: "20px", height: "20px"}) %> 
            <span>Jumlah Anak</span>
          </div>
          <small class="text-sm text-gray-500">Boleh dikosongkan</small>
          
          <input type="number" name="jumlahAnak" id="jumlahAnak" 
            class="w-full border-2 border-violet-800/50 rounded-md p-2 mt-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-violet-800 focus:border-transparent" 
            placeholder="Contoh: 10">
        </label>

        <label class="group block cursor-pointer" for="alokasiWaktu1">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-violet-800">
            <%- include('components/icons/date.ejs', {width: "20px", height: "20px"}) %> 
            <span>Alokasi Waktu</span>
          </div>
          <small class="text-sm text-gray-500">Hari &times; Jam Pelajaran</small>
          
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <input type="hidden" name="alokasiWaktu" id="alokasiWaktu" required>

            <input type="number" id="alokasiWaktu1"
            class="w-10 aspect-square border-2 border-violet-800/50 rounded-md p-2 mt-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-violet-800 focus:border-transparent" 
            placeholder="Contoh: 10" oninput="handleAlokasiWaktuChange()">
            <span>&times;</span>
            <input type="number" id="alokasiWaktu2" 
            class="w-10 aspect-square border-2 border-violet-800/50 rounded-md p-2 mt-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-violet-800 focus:border-transparent" 
            placeholder="Contoh: 10" oninput="handleAlokasiWaktuChange()">
            <span class="font-semibold mt-2">JP</span>
          </div>
          
        </label>

        <div class="group block">
          <label for="temaSubtema" class="cursor-pointer">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-sky-800">
              <%- include('components/icons/school.ejs', {width: "20px", height: "20px"}) %>
              <span>Tema/Subtema</span>
            </div>
            <small class="block text-sm text-gray-500">Tema dan Subtema yang akan diajarkan</small>
          </label>

          <div class="relative mt-2 flex items-center border-2 border-sky-800/50 rounded-md transition-all focus-within:border-sky-800 focus-within:ring-2 focus-within:ring-sky-800/50">
            <input 
              type="text" 
              name="temaSubtema" 
              id="temaSubtema"
              class="w-full border-none bg-transparent p-2.5 text-gray-700 placeholder:text-gray-400 focus:ring-0 focus:outline-none" 
              placeholder="Contoh: Keluarga / Keluargaku Sayang">

            <div class="flex items-center pr-3">
              <%- include('components/ai.ejs', {prompt: "Sempurnakan tema/subtema", type: "temaSubtemaAi"}) %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group block cursor-pointer">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-red-800">
            <%- include('components/icons/phase.ejs', {width: "20px", height: "20px"}) %> 
            <span>Model Pembelajaran</span>
          </div>
          <small class="text-sm text-gray-500">Pilih satu atau lebih pendekatan yang sesuai</small>

          <input type="hidden" name="modelPembelajaran" id="modelPembelajaran">

          <div class="mt-2 grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-red-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-red-50">
              <input type="checkbox" id="modelPembelajaranKolaboratif" class="model-pembelajaran-option accent-red-800" value="Kolaboratif">
              <span>Kolaboratif</span>
            </label>

            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-red-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-red-50">
              <input type="checkbox" id="modelPembelajaranEksperimental" class="model-pembelajaran-option accent-red-800" value="Eksperimental">
              <span>Eksperimental</span>
            </label>

            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-red-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-red-50">
              <input type="checkbox" id="modelPembelajaranBermainPeran" class="model-pembelajaran-option accent-red-800" value="Bermain Peran">
              <span>Bermain Peran</span>
            </label>

            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-red-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-red-50">
              <input type="checkbox" id="modelPembelajaranDiscoveryLearning" class="model-pembelajaran-option accent-red-800" value="Discovery Learning">
              <span>Discovery Learning</span>
            </label>

            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-red-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-red-50 sm:col-span-2">
              <input type="checkbox" id="modelPembelajaranPjBL" class="model-pembelajaran-option accent-red-800" value="Project-Based Learning (PjBL)">
              <span>Project-Based Learning (PjBL)</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group block cursor-pointer">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-red-800">
            <%- include('components/icons/phase.ejs', {width: "20px", height: "20px"}) %> 
            <span>Pilih Elemen CP</span>
          </div>
          <small class="text-sm text-gray-500">Pilih satu atau lebih elemen Capaian Pembelajaran Fase Fondasi</small>

          <input type="hidden" name="elemenCp" id="elemenCp">

          <div class="mt-2 grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-red-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-red-50">
              <input type="checkbox" id="elemenCpAgama" class="elemen-cp-option accent-red-800" value="Nilai Agama dan Budi Pekerti">
              <span>Nilai Agama dan Budi Pekerti</span>
            </label>

            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-red-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-red-50">
              <input type="checkbox" id="elemenCpJatiDiri" class="elemen-cp-option accent-red-800" value="Jati Diri">
              <span>Jati Diri</span>
            </label>

            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-red-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-red-50 sm:col-span-2">
              <input type="checkbox" id="elemenCpLiterasiSains" class="elemen-cp-option accent-red-800" value="Dasar-dasar Literasi, Matematika, Sains, Teknologi, Rekayasa, dan Seni">
              <span>Literasi-Sains-Seni</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group block cursor-pointer">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-purple-800">
            <%- include('components/icons/phase.ejs', {width: "20px", height: "20px"}) %> 
            <span>Dimensi Profil Lulusan</span>
          </div>
          <small class="text-sm text-gray-500">Pilih dimensi profil lulusan yang relevan</small>

          <input type="hidden" name="dimensiProfilLulusan" id="dimensiProfilLulusan">

          <div class="mt-2 grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-purple-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-purple-50">
              <input type="checkbox" id="dpl1" class="dpl-option accent-purple-800" value="DPL1 Keimanan dan Ketakwaan">
              <span>DPL1 Keimanan dan Ketakwaan</span>
            </label>

            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-purple-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-purple-50">
              <input type="checkbox" id="dpl2" class="dpl-option accent-purple-800" value="DPL2 Kewargaan">
              <span>DPL2 Kewargaan</span>
            </label>

            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-purple-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-purple-50">
              <input type="checkbox" id="dpl3" class="dpl-option accent-purple-800" value="DPL3 Penalaran Kritis">
              <span>DPL3 Penalaran Kritis</span>
            </label>

            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-purple-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-purple-50">
              <input type="checkbox" id="dpl4" class="dpl-option accent-purple-800" value="DPL4 Kreativitas">
              <span>DPL4 Kreativitas</span>
            </label>

            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-purple-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-purple-50">
              <input type="checkbox" id="dpl5" class="dpl-option accent-purple-800" value="DPL5 Kolaborasi">
              <span>DPL5 Kolaborasi</span>
            </label>

            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-purple-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-purple-50">
              <input type="checkbox" id="dpl6" class="dpl-option accent-purple-800" value="DPL6 Kemandirian">
              <span>DPL6 Kemandirian</span>
            </label>

            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-purple-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-purple-50">
              <input type="checkbox" id="dpl7" class="dpl-option accent-purple-800" value="DPL7 Kesehatan">
              <span>DPL7 Kesehatan</span>
            </label>

            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border-2 border-purple-800/20 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-purple-50">
              <input type="checkbox" id="dpl8" class="dpl-option accent-purple-800" value="DPL8 Komunikasi">
              <span>DPL8 Komunikasi</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group block md:col-span-2">
          <label for="tujuanPembelajaran" class="cursor-pointer">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-sky-800">
              <%- include('components/icons/school.ejs', {width: "20px", height: "20px"}) %>
              <span>Tujuan Pembelajaran</span>
            </div>
            <small class="block text-sm text-gray-500">Tulis singkat 1-2 kalimat target pembelajaran</small>
          </label>

          <div class="relative mt-2 rounded-md border-2 border-sky-800/50 transition-all focus-within:border-sky-800 focus-within:ring-2 focus-within:ring-sky-800/50">
            <textarea
              name="tujuanPembelajaran"
              id="tujuanPembelajaran"
              rows="3"
              class="w-full resize-y border-none bg-transparent p-2.5 pr-12 text-gray-700 placeholder:text-gray-400 focus:ring-0 focus:outline-none"
              placeholder="Contoh: Anak mampu menyebutkan anggota keluarganya dan menunjukkan perilaku saling menyayangi saat bermain bersama."></textarea>

            <div class="absolute right-3 top-3 flex items-center">
              <%- include('components/ai.ejs', {prompt: "Sempurnakan tujuan pembelajaran", type: "tujuanPembelajaranAi"}) %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group block">
          <label for="topikPembelajaran" class="cursor-pointer">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-green-800">
              <%- include('components/icons/user.ejs', {width: "20px", height: "20px"}) %>
              <span>Topik Pembelajaran</span>
            </div>
            <small class="block text-sm text-gray-500">Topik pendek yang spesifik untuk pekan ini</small>
          </label>

          <div class="relative mt-2 flex items-center border-2 border-green-800/50 rounded-md transition-all focus-within:border-green-800 focus-within:ring-2 focus-within:ring-green-800/50">
            <input
              type="text"
              name="topikPembelajaran"
              id="topikPembelajaran"
              class="w-full border-none bg-transparent p-2.5 text-gray-700 placeholder:text-gray-400 focus:ring-0 focus:outline-none"
              placeholder="Contoh: Aku dan Lingkungan Sekitarku">

            <div class="flex items-center pr-3">
              <%- include('components/ai.ejs', {prompt: "Sempurnakan topik pembelajaran", type: "topikPembelajaranAi"}) %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group block md:col-span-2" id="kegiatanDynamicWrapper">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-violet-800">
            <%- include('components/icons/date.ejs', {width: "20px", height: "20px"}) %>
            <span>Kegiatan Harian</span>
          </div>
          <small class="block text-sm text-gray-500">Kolom kegiatan akan otomatis dibuat berdasarkan Hari x JP pada Alokasi Waktu</small>

          <div id="kegiatanDynamicContainer" class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4"></div>
        </div>

        <template id="kegiatanAiButtonTemplate">
          <button type="button" class="bg-transparent border-0 p-0 m-0 cursor-pointer" title="AI: Sempurnakan kegiatan">
            <%- include('components/icons/bsstars.ejs', {width: "16px", height: "16px"}) %>
            <span class="sr-only">AI: Sempurnakan kegiatan</span>
          </button>
        </template>

      </div>
    </form>
  </div>
</main>

<%- include('js/home.ejs') %>
<%- include('js/dynamic-save-input.ejs') %>
